Build-Depends-Indep: debhelper (>= 4.0.2)
Standards-Version: 3.6.2.1

Package: llgal
Architecture: all
Depends: imagemagick, ${perl:Depends}, libimage-size-perl, libimage-info-perl, liburi-perl
Provides: igal
Replaces: igal, igal-text, igalwriter
Description: Online gallery generator
 llgal is a on-line gallery generator for images, videos, text and links.
 It is based on igal and adds supports for different types of slides
 including movies, text, links and subdirectories, and several options such
 as the addition of headers and footers in generated HTML files.
 Caption may be automatically generated from JPEG EXIF or GIF comments.
